{"tid":1830811,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"旺角入夜多番衝突再現私了 警扑急救員頭不顧而去","createTime":"2020-01-20T02:06:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T02:11:25.000Z","uid":248290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"65b31ad8ae47cf393b0f51c227ee9533b3ddf323","tid":1830811,"uid":248290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T02:06:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ugROZpd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FugROZpd.jpg&h=d736e759&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DO0wcKv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDO0wcKv.jpg&h=584e4366&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Py4dq4v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPy4dq4v.jpg&h=b89f0687&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iRZwXbb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiRZwXbb.jpg&h=552e7bce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sjzML4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsjzML4w.jpg&h=75734d3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nText Size 24 94<br />\n<br />\n【0119 旺角】<br />\n<br />\n2143 示威者於彌敦道及登打士街交界設置路障，途經巴士被迫停駛。一名男子下車挑釁示威者，並多次向示威者喊呼「屌你老母」，另一名男子則企圖捉著示威者。最終，兩名男子被示威者圍毆。<br />\n<br />\n2248 急救員遭警扑頭<br />\n<br />\n旺角豉油街Adidas 門外，有警員在內街內用棍扑打急救員頭部，該名急救員頭部腫起，情緒激動，不停指罵及要求該名警員出示委任證。<br />\n<br />\n2300 警員向登打士街及西洋菜南街交界推進期間，多次向記者發出警告要求他們不要阻礙推進，及後更有數名警員失控衝出向記者方向不停噴射胡椒噴霧，多名記者及路過的市民受波及，在路邊接受義務急救員救治。⠀"},{"pid":"dc1b0f4f001887bc69f76941ad2cb1d5c41e035d","tid":1830811,"uid":248290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T02:07:07.000Z","msg":"傻強 你班狗 經常失控<br />\n點攪丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ce1b96c89ffd7c261d777b56525597f5db24651","tid":1830811,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T02:11:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n1.22荔枝角收押所<br />\n1.24荔枝角收押所<br />\n1.27和你shop 彩虹戰衣</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JyA7Vuq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJyA7Vuq.jpg&h=3f02ab45&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uSBSm9r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuSBSm9r.jpg&h=fac8cfa1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2HMKXHM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2HMKXHM.png&h=a3a1e633&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OaZD19s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOaZD19s.jpg&h=065725f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">*不要屌狗 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">多聲援出庭手足</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nVq0v20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnVq0v20.jpg&h=524f4eac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加入工會<br />\ntg: hkonstrike<br />\nFB: 二百萬三罷聯合戰線<br />\n‼️連儂廁<br />\n‼️Twitter戰線"}]}